ActAn Act to amend the Geneva Conventions Act, An Act to incorporate the Canadian Red Cross Society and the Trade-marks Act
SubjectGeneva Convention ACT - Canadian Red Cross Society and Tradmarks
PrecisAN ACT TO AMEND THE GENEVA CONVENTIONS ACT, an Act to incorporate the Canadian Red Cross Society and the Trade-marks Act, Chapter 26 of the Statutes of Canada, 2007, hereby fixes January 31, 2008 as the day on which that Act comes into force.
